ck out the bridge 破坏桥梁","headword":"knock out the bridge"},{"type":"entry","text":"severed segments of the road 切断路段","headword":"severed segments of the road"},{"type":"entry","text":"be trapped in 被困在…里","headword":"be trapped in"},{"type":"entry","text":"jammed [dʒæmd]","headword":"jammed"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.卡住的"}]},{"number":1783,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"◎be jammed in陷入"},{"type":"entry","text":"disaster-relief work 救灾工作","headword":"disaster-relief work"},{"type":"entry","text":"gritter [ˈɡrɪtə(r)]","headword":"gritter"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.（冬天用于减轻路滑的）撒盐车"},{"type":"entry","text":"snow plough 扫雪机","headword":"snow plough"},{"type":"entry","text":"sledge [sledʒ]","headword":"sledge"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.雪橇"},{"type":"entry","text":"food distribution 发放食品","headword":"food distribution"},{"type":"entry","text":"take refuge 避难","headword":"take refuge"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"}]},{"number":1784,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"A：We are facing one of the largest snowstorms in the history of the"},{"type":"text","text":"city. （我们正面临这个城市有史以来最大的一场暴风雪。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Yes, the traffic was backed up by the snow. （是呀，因为这场雪"},{"type":"text","text":"交通都瘫痪了。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I locked my keys in the car, got stuck in the rain and lost my"},{"type":"text","text":"wallet. （我把钥匙锁在车里了，被困在雨中，然后把钱包也给弄丢"},{"type":"text","text":"了。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Wow, that's terrible. （呀，真是太糟糕了。）"}]}]}